WEBVTT

00:01:28.469 --> 00:01:31.657
it's probably because you didn't
know what to look for --

00:01:31.657 --> 00:01:33.032
they're everywhere.

00:01:33.032 --> 00:01:36.104
Mounted on roads or 
on police cars,

00:01:36.104 --> 00:01:40.533
Automatic License Plate Readers
capture images of every passing car

00:01:40.533 --> 00:01:44.148
and convert the license plate
into machine-readable text

00:01:44.158 --> 00:01:47.560
so that they can be checked
against hot lists

00:01:47.560 --> 00:01:50.845
of cars potentially wanted
for wrongdoing.

00:01:50.845 --> 00:01:52.972
But more than that, increasingly,

00:01:52.972 --> 00:01:55.122
local police departments 
are keeping records

00:01:55.122 --> 00:01:58.282
not just of people wanted for wrongdoing,

00:01:58.282 --> 00:02:01.084
but of every plate that 
passes them by,